        âœ… <b>ğ—›ğ—¼ğ˜„ ğ˜ğ—¼ ğ—¨ğ˜€ğ—²:</b>
        ğŸš€ Use /search <i><b>VEHICLE NUMBER</b></i> to get vehicle details.
